      | id | UserName      | GroupName |
      +----+---------------+-----------+
      |  1 | fredf         | dynamic   |
      |  2 | barney        | static    |
      |  2 | dialrouter    | netdial   |
      +----+---------------+-----------+
      3 rows in set (0.01 sec)
 
      mysql> select * from radcheck;
